translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_d00de57b:

#   rh "Nkoy Arlya was responsible for sending them, under the guise of a white flag, the Council wasn’t aware."
    rh "Nkoy Arlya fue el responsable de enviarlos, bajo la apariencia de una bandera blanca, el Consejo no estaba al tanto."

# game/episode015.rpy:295
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_a7638e91:

#   c "And why would she do that?"
    c "¿Y por qué haría eso?"

# game/episode015.rpy:300
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_13605484:

#   rh "Because Arlya is intent on seizing power for herself, she is thoroughly corrupt."
    rh "Como Arlya está decidida a hacerse con el poder, está totalmente corrompida."

# game/episode015.rpy:301
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_2776ad2e:

#   rh "About a year ago, someone came to me with incriminating information on a member of the Council."
    rh "Hace aproximadamente un año, alguien vino a mí con información incriminatoria sobre un miembro del Consejo."

# game/episode015.rpy:302
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_8ec20bf5:

#   rh "The evidence was overwhelming. Revealing wrongdoing on the part of a member of the Council would shock this world to the core."
    rh "Las pruebas eran abrumadoras. La revelación de irregularidades por parte de un miembro del Consejo conmocionaría al mundo."

# game/episode015.rpy:307
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_6121dd00:

#   rh "So I promised to investigate the matter in secret at first."
    rh "Así que prometí investigar el asunto en secreto al principio."

# game/episode015.rpy:308
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_f184909f:

#   rh "What I found confirmed the information in full."
    rh "Lo que encontré confirmó la información en su totalidad."

# game/episode015.rpy:313
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_9cd69084:

#   rh "Nkoy Arlya has been receiving considerable funds from unknown off-world parties for years."
    rh "Nkoy Arlya lleva años recibiendo fondos considerables de desconocidos de otros mundos."

# game/episode015.rpy:314
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_3d1edf44:

#   rh "She’s become very rich, but has also used her newfound wealth to destabilize our government from within."
    rh "Se ha hecho muy rica, pero también ha utilizado su nueva riqueza para desestabilizar nuestro gobierno desde dentro."

# game/episode015.rpy:315
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_47911c39:

#   rh "Her goal is to remove the ruling of the Council of Nkoy completely and establish a single leader, probably herself."
    rh "Su objetivo es eliminar por completo el gobierno del Consejo de Nkoy y establecer un único líder, probablemente ella misma."

# game/episode015.rpy:316
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_fc36b362:

#   c "And she’s doing all that right under the nose of the other Council members?"
    c "¿Y está haciendo todo eso delante de las narices de los demás miembros del Consejo?"

# game/episode015.rpy:321
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_291ac666:

#   rh "Yes, she is."
    rh "Sí, lo es."

# game/episode015.rpy:322
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_3e0aea2b:

#   rh "Arlya has long been a benefactor for all sorts of social enterprises."
    rh "Arlya es desde hace tiempo benefactora de todo tipo de empresas sociales."

# game/episode015.rpy:327
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_65882be5:

#   zi "That’s true, she is well-loved among the Cohorts."
    zi "Es cierto, es muy querida entre las Cohortes."

# game/episode015.rpy:332
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_863ecd5f:

#   rh "She has the support of many Premiers, who will undoubtedly support her rule once she is ready to declare it to the public."
    rh "Cuenta con el apoyo de muchos Primeros Ministros, que sin duda respaldarán su gobierno una vez que esté preparada para declararlo a la opinión pública."

# game/episode015.rpy:333
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_9c996621:

#   c "So she's what the Sovereignty would call a smart and well-connected politician?"
    c "¿Así que ella es lo que el Soberanismo llamaría una política inteligente y bien conectada?"

# game/episode015.rpy:338
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_cb5b5795:

#   zi "Maybe, but abolishing the Council and rule as a single leader is a thing unheard of in all of Rhenkoy history."
    zi "Tal vez, pero abolir el Consejo y gobernar como un solo líder es algo inaudito en toda la historia de Rhenkoy."

# game/episode015.rpy:339
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_ca48fa7c:

#   c "Aren't the Premiers the sole leaders of their Cohorts?"
    c "¿No son los Primeros Ministros los únicos líderes de sus Cohortes?"

# game/episode015.rpy:344
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_d9ccd538:

#   zi "Yes, they are, but the members of the Council of Nkoy are representatives chosen by all Rhenkoy."
    zi "Sí, lo son, pero los miembros del Consejo de Nkoy son representantes elegidos por todos los Rhenkoy."

# game/episode015.rpy:345
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_06bb2b9d:

#   zi "Arlya doing away with all that and attempting to establish her own rule is a break with tradition like no other."
    zi "Que Arlya acabe con todo eso e intente establecer su propia regla es una ruptura con la tradición como ninguna otra."

# game/episode015.rpy:350
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_f4e10344:

#   rh "Exactly."
    rh "Exactamente."

# game/episode015.rpy:351
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_b11e09e9:

#   rh "When I was ready to present my findings to the Council, Arlya was ready to discredit me."
    rh "Cuando estaba listo para presentar mis conclusiones al Consejo, Arlya estaba dispuesta a desacreditarme."

# game/episode015.rpy:352
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_8b9f5abe:

#   rh "She did so with gusto through an elaborate smear campaign, and I found myself slowly isolated from my peers."
    rh "Lo hizo con gusto mediante una elaborada campaña de desprestigio, y me encontré poco a poco aislado de mis compañeros."

# game/episode015.rpy:353
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_2f682cf4:

#   c "The rest of the Council just lapped up all those bad stories about you without question?"
    c "¿El resto del Consejo se tragó todas esas malas historias sobre ti sin rechistar?"

# game/episode015.rpy:358
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_f59fc79d:

#   rh "They did question, but Arlya's propaganda proved too insidious."
    rh "Lo cuestionaron, pero la propaganda de Arlya resultó demasiado insidiosa."

# game/episode015.rpy:363
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_b494d1d1:

#   zi "Rhenkoy politics, like almost everything else in our society, is bound by strict rules."
    zi "La política Rhenkoy, como casi todo en nuestra sociedad, se rige por normas estrictas."

# game/episode015.rpy:364
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_383708d8:

#   zi "Not adhering to those rules is almost unheard of."
    zi "No respetar esas normas es casi inaudito."

# game/episode015.rpy:370
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_e42aad80:

#   "Ziv looked at me intently and it made me appreciate our relationship even more."
    "Ziv me miró atentamente y eso me hizo apreciar aún más nuestra relación."

# game/episode015.rpy:371
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_184eb349:

#   "The way Ziv had brazenly thrown herself into defying the Rhenkoy's relationship tenets must have been truly something special."
    "La forma en que Ziv se había lanzado descaradamente a desafiar los principios de relación del Rhenkoy debía de ser realmente algo especial."

# game/episode015.rpy:376
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_3ffe0bae:

#   rh "Arlya is actively exploiting the honor and trust underpinning our society."
    rh "Arlya está explotando activamente el honor y la confianza que sustentan nuestra sociedad."

# game/episode015.rpy:377
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_15b5b451:

#   rh "When my accusations fell on deaf ears, I retreated from the Council."
    rh "Cuando mis acusaciones cayeron en saco roto, me retiré del Consejo."

# game/episode015.rpy:382
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_77e4c073:

#   rh "Together with my followers, I was about to mount a series of public rallies where we would let the world know what Arlya was up to."
    rh "Junto con mis seguidores, estaba a punto de organizar una serie de mítines públicos en los que daríamos a conocer al mundo lo que Arlya estaba tramando."

# game/episode015.rpy:383
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_c25babe3:

#   rh "Just before the first rally, the Council announced they were sending a team of negotiators to supposedly talk sense to me and quell any riots."
    rh "Justo antes de la primera manifestación, el Consejo anunció que iba a enviar un equipo de negociadores para, supuestamente, hacerme entrar en razón y sofocar posibles disturbios."

# game/episode015.rpy:384
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_0cfc910c:

#   rh "We were warned by several people involved in the day-to-day operations of the Council that the team they'd sent were armed and ready for violence."
    rh "Varias personas implicadas en las operaciones cotidianas del Consejo nos advirtieron de que el equipo que habían enviado iba armado y estaba preparado para la violencia."

# game/episode015.rpy:385
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_008fbd37:

#   rh "We didn't believe it at first, but prepared to defend ourselves nonetheless."
    rh "Al principio no nos lo creímos, pero aun así nos preparamos para defendernos."

# game/episode015.rpy:390
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_6d720ee9:

#   rh "And that's what we did when the team arrived, intent on murdering us."
    rh "Y eso es lo que hicimos cuando llegó el equipo, decidido a asesinarnos."

# game/episode015.rpy:391
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_74a7a217:

#   rh "My followers managed to take them by surprise and create enough of a distraction to allow us to leave and retreat here into the forest of Tand."
    rh "Mis seguidores lograron tomarlos por sorpresa y crear una distracción suficiente para permitirnos salir y retirarnos aquí, al bosque de Tand."

# game/episode015.rpy:396
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_bd8478a3:

#   c "It seems we got played."
    c "Parece que nos la han jugado."

# game/episode015.rpy:397
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_5a9687b6:

#   c "I don't very much care being used to do dirty work."
    c "No me importa mucho que me utilicen para hacer el trabajo sucio."

# game/episode015.rpy:398
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_a329f0ea:

#   c "What do you think Arlya plans to do once we bring you in?"
    c "¿Qué crees que planea hacer Arlya una vez que te traigamos?"

# game/episode015.rpy:403
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_a15072b6:

#   rh "There's a reason why she went behind the backs of her fellow Council members, so I doubt it will be anything positive."
    rh "Por algo fue a espaldas de sus compañeros del Consejo, así que dudo que sea algo positivo."

# game/episode015.rpy:404
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_87886854:

#   c "Say I want to become involved in the wonderful world of Rhenkoy politics, what would you have me do?"
    c "Digamos que quiero involucrarme en el maravilloso mundo de la política Rhenkoy, ¿qué quieres que haga?"

# game/episode015.rpy:405
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_c1ff83ba:

#   rh "Bring me to the capital like you were ordered, but allow me to speak to the Council instead of handing me into the custody of Nkoy Arlya."
    rh "Llévame a la capital como se te ordenó, pero permíteme hablar con el Consejo en lugar de entregarme a la custodia de Nkoy Arlya."

# game/episode015.rpy:406
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_e1490063:

#   rh "I will make a speech to denounce Arlya and present the evidence I had gathered."
    rh "Haré un discurso para denunciar a Arlya y presentar las pruebas que he reunido."

# game/episode015.rpy:407
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_9e6fd299:

#   rh "The revelation that she has recruited clandestine off-world help will only strengthen my narrative."
    rh "La revelación de que ha reclutado ayuda clandestina fuera del mundo sólo fortalecerá mi narrativa."

# game/episode015.rpy:410
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_80d648a6:

#   c "That all sounds dreadful enough, but I can't afford to become involved."
    c "Todo eso suena bastante terrible, pero no puedo permitirme involucrarme."

# game/episode015.rpy:415
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_e0df65b3:

#   rh "The integrity of Rhenkoy leadership is at grave risk, I beg you to reconsider your involvement."
    rh "La integridad de la dirección de Rhenkoy está en grave peligro, le ruego que reconsidere su participación."

# game/episode015.rpy:416
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_8d918456:

#   c "Sorry, but I can't risk losing Arlya's promised reward."
    c "Lo siento, pero no puedo arriesgarme a perder la recompensa prometida de Arlya."

# game/episode015.rpy:421
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_8116ead9:

#   rh "And what reward is that, money?"
    rh "¿Y qué recompensa es esa, dinero?"

# game/episode015.rpy:422
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_7cde8f47:

#   c "Nothing so banal."
    c "Nada tan banal."

# game/episode015.rpy:423
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_de4b820d:

#   c "Arlya has promised us access to some Scolguin prisoners."
    c "Arlya nos ha prometido acceso a algunos prisioneros Scolguin."

# game/episode015.rpy:424
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_b002c2cc:

#   rh "What if I promise you the same thing?"
    rh "¿Y si te prometo lo mismo?"

# game/episode015.rpy:425
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_a0759d58:

#   c "You'd allow us to interrogate the Scolguin soldiers in return for helping to overthrow Arlya?"
    c "¿Nos permitirías interrogar a los soldados Scolguin a cambio de ayudar a derrocar a Arlya?"

# game/episode015.rpy:426
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_974fcaf7:

#   rh "Yes, I would."
    rh "Sí, me gustaría."

# game/episode015.rpy:430
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_4dc10237:

#   c "It's a gamble, but one I'm willing to take."
    c "Es una apuesta arriesgada, pero estoy dispuesto a hacerla."

# game/episode015.rpy:435
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_dc62ca42:

#   rh "Excellent!"
    rh "¡Excelente!"

# game/episode015.rpy:436
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_4bcb2997:

#   c "What would you have us do?"
    c "¿Qué quiere que hagamos?"

# game/episode015.rpy:447
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_652165aa:

#   c "I'm afraid I still can't take that risk."
    c "Me temo que aún no puedo correr ese riesgo."

# game/episode015.rpy:448
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_94484f87:

#   c "Arlya currently has the power to grant us access, whereas you are still viewed as a rebel and a threat."
    c "Arlya tiene actualmente el poder de concedernos acceso, mientras que a ti se te sigue considerando un rebelde y una amenaza."

# game/episode015.rpy:453
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_edc0d8bf:

#   rh "How disappointing, but I shouldn't have expected any less from mercenaries like you."
    rh "Qué decepción, pero no debería haber esperado menos de mercenarios como tú."

# game/episode015.rpy:454
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_62fd832a:

#   rh "I hope you can live with the choices of your commander..."
    rh "Espero que pueda vivir con las decisiones de su comandante..."

# game/episode015.rpy:455
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_bb8ec118:

#   zi "I..."
    zi "I..."

# game/episode015.rpy:441
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_c1ff83ba_1:

#   rh "Bring me to the capital like you were ordered, but allow me to speak to the Council instead of handing me into the custody of Nkoy Arlya."
    rh "Llévame a la capital como se te ordenó, pero permíteme hablar con el Consejo en lugar de entregarme a la custodia de Nkoy Arlya."

# game/episode015.rpy:442
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_e1490063_1:

#   rh "I will make a speech to denounce Arlya and present the evidence I had gathered."
    rh "Haré un discurso para denunciar a Arlya y presentar las pruebas que he reunido."

# game/episode015.rpy:443
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_explanation_9e6fd299_1:

#   rh "The revelation that she has recruited clandestine off-world help will only strengthen my narrative."
    rh "La revelación de que ha reclutado ayuda clandestina fuera del mundo sólo fortalecerá mi narrativa."

# game/episode015.rpy:460
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_help_8438473d:

#   c "We’re placing a lot of faith in you, Nkoy Rhedia, I sure hope this gamble will pay off."
    c "Confiamos mucho en ti, Nkoy Rhedia, espero que esta apuesta dé sus frutos."

# game/episode015.rpy:465
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_help_6af8b983:

#   rh "I will do my very best to help you and I have confidence in the Council to see reason."
    rh "Haré todo lo posible por ayudarle y confío en que el Consejo entre en razón."

# game/episode015.rpy:466
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_help_8e5c1374:

#   c "Night will be falling soon."
    c "Pronto caerá la noche."

# game/episode015.rpy:467
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_help_a433c4a2:

#   c "We’ll head out in the morning."
    c "Saldremos por la mañana."

# game/episode015.rpy:468
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_help_d11fbe7f:

#   c "Despite your promises we’ll have to keep you under guard, I hope you understand."
    c "A pesar de tus promesas tendremos que mantenerte bajo vigilancia, espero que lo entiendas."

# game/episode015.rpy:469
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_help_fe96cc7f:

#   rh "I do."
    rh "A mí sí."

# game/episode015.rpy:472
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_help_5692f008:

#   rh "Will you allow my followers to retrieve our fallen comrades from the forest?"
    rh "¿Permitirás que mis seguidores recuperen a nuestros camaradas caídos del bosque?"

# game/episode015.rpy:473
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_help_4e8c7062:

#   c "Of course."
    c "Por supuesto."

# game/episode015.rpy:478
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_help_21dfb2dd:

#   rh "I will ask my people to assign your lodgings for the night."
    rh "Pediré a mi gente que le asigne alojamiento para esta noche."

# game/episode015.rpy:483
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_help_3c503cf7:

#   zi "That’s very kind of you, Nkoy Rhedia."
    zi "Eres muy amable, Nkoy Rhedia."

# game/episode015.rpy:485
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_help_048323e5:

#   "The followers of Rhedia were a little apprehensive of us at first and stayed out of our way mostly."
    "Al principio, los seguidores de Rhedia se mostraron un poco recelosos y se mantuvieron alejados de nosotros."

# game/episode015.rpy:487
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_help_5e1784c5:

#   "We agreed on taking turns on guard duty and retired for the night."
    "Acordamos turnarnos en las guardias y nos retiramos a dormir."

# game/episode015.rpy:493
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_decline_f5d844e8:

#   c "Kit, take her inside."
    c "Kit, llévala adentro."

# game/episode015.rpy:494
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_decline_94f8537d:

#   "Resigned, Nkoy Rhedia followed Kit inside her yurt."
    "Resignada, Nkoy Rhedia siguió a Kit al interior de su yurta."

# game/episode015.rpy:496
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_decline_a31ba740:

#   c "Kit?"
    c "¿Kit?"

# game/episode015.rpy:498
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_decline_e20a2642:

#   ki "Yeah?"
    ki "¿Sí?"

# game/episode015.rpy:499
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_decline_d65a1ebe:

#   c "Take her away."
    c "Llévatela."

# game/episode015.rpy:500
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_decline_1449ccfe:

#   ki "Of course."
    ki "Por supuesto."

# game/episode015.rpy:503
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_decline_8e5c1374:

#   c "Night will be falling soon."
    c "Pronto caerá la noche."

# game/episode015.rpy:504
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_decline_2fd1be8d:

#   c "I suggest we confiscate a few of these tents and spend the night."
    c "Sugiero que confisquemos algunas de estas tiendas y pasemos la noche."

# game/episode015.rpy:506
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_decline_776d8573:

#   av "Is that safe?"
    av "¿Es seguro?"

# game/episode015.rpy:507
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_decline_4244aee9:

#   c "Yes, we’ll take turns on guard duty."
    c "Sí, haremos turnos de guardia."

# game/episode015.rpy:508
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_decline_756f7683:

#   c "Considering the resistance we’ve encountered so far, I don’t think we’ll be in any considerable danger."
    c "Teniendo en cuenta la resistencia que hemos encontrado hasta ahora, no creo que corramos un peligro considerable."

# game/episode015.rpy:509
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_decline_c8e41591:

#   c "Come morning, we’ll head back out to the Bastard."
    c "Por la mañana, volveremos al Bastardo."

# game/episode015.rpy:511
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_decline_ef119574:

#   "The remaining people in the encampment stayed out of our way and we retired for the night in peace."
    "El resto de la gente del campamento se apartó de nuestro camino y nos retiramos a dormir en paz."

# game/episode015.rpy:502
translate spanish ep015_rhedia_decline_94f8537d_1:

#   "Resigned, Nkoy Rhedia followed Kit inside her yurt."
    "Resignada, Nkoy Rhedia siguió a Kit al interior de su yurta."

# game/episode015.rpy:520
translate spanish ep015_camp_ziv_61dcfb08:

#   zi "I just wanted to see you before I go to bed."
    zi "Sólo quería verte antes de irme a la cama."

# game/episode015.rpy:522
translate spanish ep015_camp_ziv_a6341296:

#   zi "I wanted to speak to you for a moment."
    zi "Quería hablar contigo un momento."

# game/episode015.rpy:523
translate spanish ep015_camp_ziv_4e8c7062:

#   c "Of course."
    c "Por supuesto."

# game/episode015.rpy:525
translate spanish ep015_camp_ziv_e42a12a1:

#   zi "I don't like what we did today, [p_name]."
    zi "No me gusta lo que hicimos hoy, [p_name]."

# game/episode015.rpy:526
translate spanish ep015_camp_ziv_1ece7c5f:

#   c "Yes, you've made that clear enough."
    c "Sí, lo ha dejado suficientemente claro."

# game/episode015.rpy:528
translate spanish ep015_camp_ziv_388b97a0:

#   zi "What was I to do?!"
    zi "¿Qué iba a hacer?"

# game/episode015.rpy:529
translate spanish ep015_camp_ziv_1cc2798b:

#   zi "Kill that defenseless woman?!"
    zi "¡¿Matar a esa mujer indefensa?!"

# game/episode015.rpy:530
translate spanish ep015_camp_ziv_26eefe0a:

#   c "Yes."
    c "Sí."

# game/episode015.rpy:531
translate spanish ep015_camp_ziv_06ee06e4:

#   zi "How can you say that?"
    zi "¿Cómo puedes decir eso?"

# game/episode015.rpy:532
translate spanish ep015_camp_ziv_d09e60e2:

#   c "Because you've endangered all of us by not following orders."
    c "Porque nos has puesto en peligro a todos al no seguir las órdenes."

# game/episode015.rpy:533
