    "Eva no mostraba signos externos de angustia, mientras su cabeza reposaba en el regazo de Lilly."

# game/episode015.rpy:705
translate spanish ep015_bastard_e355a417:

#   l "We have to do something, she's been like this for hours."
    l "Tenemos que hacer algo, lleva así horas."

# game/episode015.rpy:707
translate spanish ep015_bastard_e7a17990:

#   "Jade got to work on the simulation's console."
    "Jade se puso a trabajar en la consola de la simulación."

# game/episode015.rpy:708
translate spanish ep015_bastard_7bfd7098:

#   c "She hasn't been conscious after she entered the simulation?"
    c "¿No ha estado consciente después de entrar en la simulación?"

# game/episode015.rpy:710
translate spanish ep015_bastard_4fc20161:

#   l "No, we heard her scream and found her lying on the floor here."
    l "No, la oímos gritar y la encontramos aquí tirada en el suelo."

# game/episode015.rpy:711
translate spanish ep015_bastard_57cd37f0:

#   l "Do you know what's the matter [p_name_short]?"
    l "¿Sabes lo que pasa [p_name_short]?"

# game/episode015.rpy:712
translate spanish ep015_bastard_1c9a96c3:

#   c "It can't be good, whatever it is."
    c "No puede ser bueno, sea lo que sea."

# game/episode015.rpy:713
translate spanish ep015_bastard_a4a18ce4:

#   c "Any luck, Jade?"
    c "¿Ha habido suerte, Jade?"

# game/episode015.rpy:715
translate spanish ep015_bastard_3a56e9e4:

#   j "No, there's no way to separate her from the simulation without causing massive damage, like Thyia already said."
    j "No, no hay forma de separarla de la simulación sin causar daños masivos, como ya dijo Thyia."

# game/episode015.rpy:716
translate spanish ep015_bastard_0a830946:

#   c "Fuck!"
    c "¡Joder!"

# game/episode015.rpy:717
translate spanish ep015_bastard_744321c3:

#   j "Someone could go in though and try to free her from within the simulation."
    j "Sin embargo, alguien podría entrar e intentar liberarla desde dentro de la simulación."

# game/episode015.rpy:718
translate spanish ep015_bastard_2f81e0b2:

#   c "That sounds like a plan, I'll do it."
    c "Me parece un buen plan, lo haré."

# game/episode015.rpy:719
translate spanish ep015_bastard_243b4778:

#   j "I have to warn you though, it could be very dangerous."
    j "Pero tengo que advertirte de que puede ser muy peligroso."

# game/episode015.rpy:720
translate spanish ep015_bastard_33251b34:

#   j "Whatever is keeping Eva stuck inside could do the same to you."
    j "Lo que sea que mantiene a Eva atrapada en su interior podría hacer lo mismo contigo."

# game/episode015.rpy:721
translate spanish ep015_bastard_ffd0c398:

#   c "I'll take that risk."
    c "Correré ese riesgo."

# game/episode015.rpy:723
translate spanish ep015_bastard_acecbbb3:

#   l "I'm coming with."
    l "Ya voy."

# game/episode015.rpy:724
translate spanish ep015_bastard_0b0f14f5:

#   c "No Lilly, I can't let you do that."
    c "No Lilly, no puedo dejarte hacer eso."

# game/episode015.rpy:727
translate spanish ep015_bastard_18a843ae:

#   l "But she's my sister too!"
    l "¡Pero también es mi hermana!"

# game/episode015.rpy:729
translate spanish ep015_bastard_d0c11312:

#   l "But she's my friend too!"
    l "¡Pero también es mi amiga!"

# game/episode015.rpy:730
translate spanish ep015_bastard_57644027:

#   c "I know, but we can't risk two people getting stuck with Eva in there."
    c "Lo sé, pero no podemos arriesgarnos a que dos personas se queden atrapadas con Eva ahí dentro."

# game/episode015.rpy:731
translate spanish ep015_bastard_3f531d11:

#   c "I'm partially responsible for this mess, so I'll fix it."
    c "Soy parcialmente responsable de este desastre, así que lo arreglaré."

# game/episode015.rpy:733
translate spanish ep015_bastard_c311fdc0:

#   l "Okay...{w} but hurry!"
    l "Bueno...{w} ¡pero date prisa!"

# game/episode015.rpy:734
translate spanish ep015_bastard_255ecca1:

#   c "I will."
    c "Lo haré."

# game/episode015.rpy:735
translate spanish ep015_bastard_099d45ce:

#   c "Tell Céline not to take off before Eva and me are back."
    c "Dile a Céline que no se vaya antes de que Eva y yo volvamos."

# game/episode015.rpy:737
translate spanish ep015_bastard_e8462428:

#   j "Got it."
    j "Entendido."

# game/episode015.rpy:739
translate spanish ep015_bastard_55b8aa80:

#   c "Going in now."
    c "Entrando ahora."

# game/episode015.rpy:743
translate spanish ep015_bastard_23f06094:

#   "We climbed aboard, and I directed Aven and Kit to escort Rhedia to the guest quarters."
    "Subimos a bordo, e indiqué a Aven y Kit que escoltaran a Rhedia hasta los camarotes de invitados."

# game/episode015.rpy:745
translate spanish ep015_bastard_3354aa5b:

#   "We climbed aboard, and I directed Aven and Kit to escort Rhedia to the brig."
    "Subimos a bordo y ordené a Aven y Kit que escoltaran a Rhedia hasta el calabozo."

# game/episode015.rpy:752
translate spanish ep015_sim_375db71f:

#   "As soon as the familiar surroundings of Tuolovi materialized around me, I felt something was off."
    "En cuanto el entorno familiar de Tuolovi se materializó a mi alrededor, sentí que algo no iba bien."

# game/episode015.rpy:753
translate spanish ep015_sim_e7d9065f:

#   "A wrongness permeated the entire estate."
    "Un mal impregnaba toda la finca."

# game/episode015.rpy:755
translate spanish ep015_sim_a706fb1f:

#   "The grounds, once lush and green, were now dry and barren."
    "Los terrenos, antes frondosos y verdes, estaban ahora secos y estériles."

# game/episode015.rpy:757
translate spanish ep015_sim_3536c6a6:

#   "The house itself radiated an eerie light."
    "La propia casa irradiaba una luz espeluznante."

# game/episode015.rpy:758
translate spanish ep015_sim_5e472544:

#   "During my earlier visits, the house hadn't felt truly lived in, now it seemed desolate."
    "Durante mis visitas anteriores, la casa no había parecido realmente habitada, ahora parecía desolada."

# game/episode015.rpy:759
translate spanish ep015_sim_3a038e4b:

#   "I proceeded with caution."
    "Procedí con cautela."

# game/episode015.rpy:760
translate spanish ep015_sim_cc19c357:

#   "Whatever had trapped an unsuspecting Eva inside would probably be waiting for me."
    "Lo que hubiera atrapado a una Eva desprevenida dentro, probablemente estaría esperándome."

# game/episode015.rpy:761
translate spanish ep015_sim_e76dc923:

#   "I crossed the grounds towards the entrance of the house and tried the door."
    "Crucé el terreno hacia la entrada de la casa y probé la puerta."

# game/episode015.rpy:763
translate spanish ep015_sim_0f44f46b:

#   "It was unlocked."
    "Estaba desbloqueado."

# game/episode015.rpy:764
translate spanish ep015_sim_14339fad:

#   "Softly, I opened the door and made my way inside."
    "Suavemente, abrí la puerta y entré."

# game/episode015.rpy:766
translate spanish ep015_sim_7d28c550:

#   "The interior of the house wasn't exactly in disrepair, but everything was cast in an unnatural light, coming from everywhere and nowhere in particular."
    "El interior de la casa no estaba precisamente en mal estado, pero todo estaba envuelto en una luz antinatural, procedente de todas partes y de ninguna en particular."

# game/episode015.rpy:767
translate spanish ep015_sim_407544d5:

#   "The entire mansion was utterly silent."
    "Toda la mansión estaba en absoluto silencio."

# game/episode015.rpy:768
translate spanish ep015_sim_3a213479:

#   "I didn't find any traces of someone living inside the house."
    "No encontré ningún rastro de alguien viviendo dentro de la casa."

# game/episode015.rpy:769
translate spanish ep015_sim_550706ba:

#   "Hesitantly, I made my way to the stairs, back to the bedroom where I'd left Lilly and Eva last time."
    "Vacilante, me dirigí a las escaleras, de vuelta al dormitorio donde había dejado a Lilly y Eva la última vez."

# game/episode015.rpy:771
translate spanish ep015_sim_09cd2f27:

#   "All of the upstairs doors were closed and the hallway seemed as empty as the downstairs rooms."
    "Todas las puertas de arriba estaban cerradas y el pasillo parecía tan vacío como las habitaciones de abajo."

# game/episode015.rpy:773
translate spanish ep015_sim_382900dd:

#   "When I was about to try the door to Eva's bedroom, a voice spoke behind me."
    "Cuando estaba a punto de intentar abrir la puerta del dormitorio de Eva, una voz habló detrás de mí."

# game/episode015.rpy:775
translate spanish ep015_sim_d985ddaf:

#   l "You've returned."
    l "Has vuelto."

# game/episode015.rpy:782
translate spanish ep015_sim_0c7c9728:

#   "I turned around and faced my sister."
    "Me di la vuelta y me enfrenté a mi hermana."

# game/episode015.rpy:784
translate spanish ep015_sim_e406ec8e:

#   "I turned around and faced Lilly."
    "Me di la vuelta y me enfrenté a Lilly."

# game/episode015.rpy:792
translate spanish ep015_sim_d6932ab9:

#   l "Eva, [p_name_short], are you all right?"
    l "Eva, [p_name_short]¿Estás bien?"

# game/episode015.rpy:793
translate spanish ep015_sim_058dd7b5:

#   c "Yes, I think so."
    c "Sí, creo que sí."

# game/episode015.rpy:796
translate spanish ep015_sim_6d0e7063:

#   j "It might be better if Thim had a look at Eva."
    j "Sería mejor que Thim echara un vistazo a Eva."

# game/episode015.rpy:798
translate spanish ep015_sim_67135a15:

#   j "It might be better if the autodoc had a look at Eva."
    j "Sería mejor que el autodoc le echara un vistazo a Eva."

# game/episode015.rpy:800
translate spanish ep015_sim_b18a6c0a:

#   l "I'll take her to the medbay."
    l "La llevaré a la enfermería."

# game/episode015.rpy:801
translate spanish ep015_sim_415723d9:

#   l "Can you walk, Eva?"
    l "¿Puedes caminar, Eva?"

# game/episode015.rpy:803
translate spanish ep015_sim_eafbc7bb:

#   e "Y-Yes, I think so."
    e "S-Sí, creo que sí."

# game/episode015.rpy:804
translate spanish ep015_sim_9e168798:

#   e "What happened?"
    e "¿Qué ha pasado?"

# game/episode015.rpy:805
translate spanish ep015_sim_9947415f:

#   c "I'll explain later, once you've had your checkup."
    c "Te lo explicaré más tarde, cuando te hayas hecho la revisión."

# game/episode015.rpy:806
translate spanish ep015_sim_d2a74119:

#   e "Okay, that sounds good, I guess."
    e "Vale, eso suena bien, supongo."

# game/episode015.rpy:809
translate spanish ep015_sim_2df6e0bd:

#   j "What do you want me to do with the simulation?"
    j "¿Qué quieres que haga con la simulación?"

# game/episode015.rpy:810
translate spanish ep015_sim_61916c5a:

#   c "Keep it running indefinitely, but make sure that nobody can access it by accident."
    c "Mantenlo en funcionamiento indefinidamente, pero asegúrate de que nadie pueda acceder a él por accidente."

# game/episode015.rpy:811
translate spanish ep015_sim_5e4ace8e:

#   j "Of course."
    j "Por supuesto."

# game/episode015.rpy:812
translate spanish ep015_sim_dc39f861:

#   j "I've never seen anyone respond so badly in a simulation, what was in there anyway?"
    j "Nunca había visto a nadie responder tan mal en una simulación, ¿qué había ahí dentro?"

# game/episode015.rpy:813
translate spanish ep015_sim_48179aab:

#   c "Things better left undisturbed."
    c "Cosas que es mejor no tocar."

# game/episode015.rpy:816
translate spanish ep015_sim_f6866f70:

#   c "Delete all trace of it."
    c "Borra todo rastro de ella."

# game/episode015.rpy:817
translate spanish ep015_sim_bb6021aa:

#   j "Understood."
    j "Entendido."

# game/episode015.rpy:819
translate spanish ep015_sim_af40740f:

#   c "Very bad stuff."
    c "Cosas muy malas."

# game/episode015.rpy:820
translate spanish ep015_sim_868640c3:

#   c "The rest of the system should be unaffected, though."
    c "Sin embargo, el resto del sistema no debería verse afectado."

# game/episode015.rpy:821
translate spanish ep015_sim_d9865933:

#   c "Now, if you don't mind, I'd like to be alone in my quarters for a while."
    c "Ahora, si no te importa, me gustaría estar solo en mis aposentos un rato."

# game/episode015.rpy:822
translate spanish ep015_sim_a52dc35f:

#   c "Tell Céline we're ready to go."
    c "Dile a Céline que estamos listos para irnos."

# game/episode015.rpy:824
translate spanish ep015_sim_c7763b6f:

#   th "Understood."
    th "Entendido."

# game/episode015.rpy:831
translate spanish ep015_sim_0306d026:

#   l "I had such bad dreams last night."
    l "Tuve pesadillas anoche."

# game/episode015.rpy:833
translate spanish ep015_sim_987e3d37:

#   e "Really?"
    e "¿De verdad?"

# game/episode015.rpy:834
translate spanish ep015_sim_224b33c7:

#   e "I can't remember a thing from last night."
    e "No recuerdo nada de anoche."

# game/episode015.rpy:836
translate spanish ep015_sim_087166f0:

#   l "You had passed away and in the middle of mourning, [p_name] had gotten back here."
    l "Habías fallecido y en medio del duelo, [p_name] había vuelto aquí."

# game/episode015.rpy:837
translate spanish ep015_sim_8ca093d7:

#   l "From the Academy, I guess?"
    l "¿De la Academia, supongo?"

# game/episode015.rpy:838
translate spanish ep015_sim_1ff9df48:

#   l "We had a terrible fight."
    l "Tuvimos una pelea terrible."

# game/episode015.rpy:839
translate spanish ep015_sim_dacaf6d8:

#   e "Well, I'm still here."
    e "Bueno, sigo aquí."

# game/episode015.rpy:840
translate spanish ep015_sim_720bdbf6:

#   l "Yeah, I know."
    l "Sí, lo sé."

# game/episode015.rpy:841
translate spanish ep015_sim_c6b3f639:

#   l "It was just a dream, but it felt so real."
    l "Era sólo un sueño, pero parecía tan real."

# game/episode015.rpy:843
translate spanish ep015_sim_9560dbd2:

#   e "I hate dreams like that."
    e "Odio los sueños así."

# game/episode015.rpy:844
translate spanish ep015_sim_28f19e23:

#   l "Yeah, me too."
    l "Sí, yo también."

# game/episode015.rpy:845
translate spanish ep015_sim_63e5d9b3:

#   l "But enough about that."
    l "Pero basta ya."

# game/episode015.rpy:847
translate spanish ep015_sim_286d86b3:

#   l "It's a beautiful day and we're going to enjoy it, you and I."
    l "Hace un día precioso y vamos a disfrutarlo, tú y yo."

# game/episode015.rpy:848
translate spanish ep015_sim_a37b796c:

#   e "Sounds like a great plan."
    e "Me parece un plan estupendo."

# game/episode015.rpy:850
translate spanish ep015_sim_0fb12215:

#   e "Poor [p_name_short], holed up at the Academy."
    e "Pobre [p_name_short], encerrado en la Academia."

# game/episode015.rpy:851
translate spanish ep015_sim_5f7b6e29:

#   e "I'm so glad we don't have to go and just enjoy our lives here."
    e "Estoy muy contenta de no tener que ir y poder disfrutar de nuestra vida aquí."

# game/episode015.rpy:852
translate spanish ep015_sim_a76bfadf:

#   l "I'm sure he'll be back some time."
    l "Estoy seguro de que volverá en algún momento."

# game/episode015.rpy:854
translate spanish ep015_sim_6ce2c128:

#   e "Yeah, some time."
    e "Sí, alguna vez."

# game/episode015.rpy:855
translate spanish ep015_sim_3e98efdd:

#   e "The garden is looking extra pretty right now, let's enjoy the sun there."
    e "El jardín está muy bonito ahora, disfrutemos del sol."

# game/episode015.rpy:863
translate spanish ep015_sim_9e280f00:

#   e "Me too."
    e "A mí también."

# game/episode015.rpy:864
translate spanish ep015_sim_f86a62b9:

#   l "We were in a bitter fight."
    l "Estábamos en una lucha encarnizada."

# game/episode015.rpy:865
translate spanish ep015_sim_e184000a:

#   e "Yes, a bitter fight...{w} over him."
    e "Sí, una lucha amarga ... {w} por él."

# game/episode015.rpy:866
translate spanish ep015_sim_99ae4b2f:

#   l "You dreamt the same thing?"
    l "¿Soñaste lo mismo?"

# game/episode015.rpy:867
translate spanish ep015_sim_b841d111:

#   e "I think so."
    e "Creo que sí."

# game/episode015.rpy:869
translate spanish ep015_sim_c79e1b06:

#   e "It must be because we loved him both so dearly."
    e "Debe ser porque le queríamos tanto."

# game/episode015.rpy:870
translate spanish ep015_sim_83530090:

#   e "And now he's gone..."
    e "Y ahora se ha ido..."

# game/episode015.rpy:871
translate spanish ep015_sim_0e55bc49:

#   l "I still can't believe it."
    l "Todavía no me lo creo."

# game/episode015.rpy:872
translate spanish ep015_sim_5bb80a41:

#   e "Me neither."
    e "Yo tampoco."

# game/episode015.rpy:874
translate spanish ep015_sim_72e75ef3:

#   e "At least we still have each other."
    e "Al menos aún nos tenemos el uno al otro."

# game/episode015.rpy:875
translate spanish ep015_sim_e2a940ee:

#   l "Fortunately."
    l "Afortunadamente."

# game/episode015.rpy:878
translate spanish ep015_sim_1138628b:

#   "The sisters exchanged a kiss that lingered definitively into the realm of impropriety."
    "Las hermanas intercambiaron un beso que entró definitivamente en el terreno de lo inapropiado."

# game/episode015.rpy:880
translate spanish ep015_sim_504bbf05:

#   "The girls exchanged a kiss that lingered definitively into the realm of impropriety."
    "Las chicas intercambiaron un beso que entró definitivamente en el terreno de lo inapropiado."

# game/episode015.rpy:882
translate spanish ep015_sim_e1b17a7c:

#   l "Do you want me to come to your room tonight again?"
    l "¿Quieres que vaya a tu habitación esta noche otra vez?"

# game/episode015.rpy:883
translate spanish ep015_sim_29f9af9a:

#   e "Yes, I'd like that very much."
    e "Sí, me gustaría mucho."

# game/episode015.rpy:884
translate spanish ep015_sim_76d2c532:

#   l "I love you, Eva."
    l "Te quiero, Eva."

# game/episode015.rpy:885
translate spanish ep015_sim_967e729a:

#   e "I love you too, Lilly."
    e "Yo también te quiero, Lilly."

# game/episode015.rpy:890
translate spanish ep015_sim_f09489f5:

#   l "I know it's been a while since I visited."
    l "Sé que hace tiempo que no te visito."

# game/episode015.rpy:892
translate spanish ep015_sim_2427dabf:

#   l "I miss you, dearest brother."
    l "Te echo de menos, querido hermano."

# game/episode015.rpy:894
translate spanish ep015_sim_bd0182c9:

#   l "I miss you, dearest."
    l "Te echo de menos, querida."

# game/episode015.rpy:896
translate spanish ep015_sim_d2e513e9:

#   l "You might be interested to know that I visited Eva's grave."
    l "Te interesará saber que visité la tumba de Eva."

# game/episode015.rpy:897
translate spanish ep015_sim_878fe452:

#   l "You know what I did?"
    l "¿Sabes lo que hice?"

# game/episode015.rpy:899
translate spanish ep015_sim_665d88e5:

#   l "I pissed all over it."
    l "Me he meado encima."

# game/episode015.rpy:900
translate spanish ep015_sim_97034daf:

#   l "Haha, yes I did!"
    l "Jaja, ¡sí!"

# game/episode015.rpy:902
translate spanish ep015_sim_b83219a5:

#   l "I know, I know, I'm talking to myself too much."
    l "Lo sé, lo sé, hablo demasiado solo."

# game/episode015.rpy:903
translate spanish ep015_sim_2fc771aa:

#   l "I wish you were here, taking me in your strong arms."
    l "Desearía que estuvieras aquí, tomándome en tus fuertes brazos."

# game/episode015.rpy:905
translate spanish ep015_sim_fa5a36d1:

#   l "Just thinking of you gets me all going."
    l "Sólo de pensar en ti me pongo las pilas."

# game/episode015.rpy:907
translate spanish ep015_sim_1aa32914:

#   l "I'm sure that you won't mind if I enjoy myself a little here."
    l "Estoy seguro de que no te importará que me divierta un poco aquí."

# game/episode015.rpy:909
translate spanish ep015_sim_1cc22827:

#   l "That's right."
    l "Así es."

# game/episode015.rpy:910
translate spanish ep015_sim_b9796a3c:

#   l "Oh [p_name_short]!"
    l "Oh [p_name_short]!"

# game/episode015.rpy:911
translate spanish ep015_sim_c22d672a:

#   l "Yes, right there!"
    l "¡Sí, justo ahí!"

# game/episode015.rpy:916
translate spanish ep015_sim_d5beeceb:

#   l "Hey you two."
    l "Hola a los dos."

# game/episode015.rpy:917
translate spanish ep015_sim_392d704a:

#   l "I had such a bad dream last night."
    l "Tuve una pesadilla anoche."

# game/episode015.rpy:919
translate spanish ep015_sim_30f8225c:

#   l "Eva and I, we were both fighting over you, [p_name]."
    l "Eva y yo, los dos estábamos peleando por ti, [p_name]."

# game/episode015.rpy:920
translate spanish ep015_sim_5f075462:

#   l "Yes, fighting over him, can you imagine, Eva?"
    l "Sí, peleando por él, ¿te imaginas, Eva?"

# game/episode015.rpy:921
translate spanish ep015_sim_36c9be86:

#   l "When I woke up, I had a realization."
    l "Cuando me desperté, me di cuenta."

# game/episode015.rpy:923
translate spanish ep015_sim_f92028b2:

#   l "Was [p_name] leaving the reason why you chose to end things, Eva?"
    l "Era [p_name] ¿dejando la razón por la que elegiste terminar las cosas, Eva?"

# game/episode015.rpy:925
translate spanish ep015_sim_ab0c0c39:

#   l "I guess I'll never know."
    l "Supongo que nunca lo sabré."

# game/episode015.rpy:926
translate spanish ep015_sim_ce1a3491:

#   l "Sorry for talking to myself so much, but it gets pretty lonely here without you two being there."
    l "Perdón por hablar tanto solo, pero me siento muy solo aquí sin vosotros dos."

# game/episode015.rpy:927
translate spanish ep015_sim_f6bd9e24:

#   l "I'll keep visiting your graves, if you don't mind."
    l "Seguiré visitando vuestras tumbas, si no os importa."

# game/episode015.rpy:929
translate spanish ep015_sim_2e3e4187:

#   l "I guess you don't..."
    l "Supongo que no..."

# game/episode015.rpy:815
translate spanish ep015_sim_2df6e0bd_1:

#   j "What do you want me to do with the simulation?"
    j "¿Qué quieres que haga con la simulación?"

# game/episode015.rpy:818
translate spanish ep015_sim_dc39f861_1:

#   j "I've never seen anyone respond so badly in a simulation, what was in there anyway?"
    j "Nunca había visto a nadie responder tan mal en una simulación, ¿qué había ahí dentro?"

# game/episode015.rpy:860
translate spanish ep015_sim_0306d026_1:

#   l "I had such bad dreams last night."
    l "Tuve pesadillas anoche."

# game/episode015.rpy:862
translate spanish ep015_sim_987e3d37_1:

#   e "Really?"
    e "¿De verdad?"

# game/episode015.rpy:937
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_445a3556:

#   "She wasn't wearing much and seemed very much aware of the effect it had on me."
    "No llevaba mucha ropa y parecía muy consciente del efecto que tenía en mí."

# game/episode015.rpy:939
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_268e6ec2:

#   "Lilly came closer, her movements carefully choreographed to enhance the effect of the clinging dress as much as possible."
    "Lilly se acercó, sus movimientos cuidadosamente coreografiados para realzar al máximo el efecto del ceñido vestido."

# game/episode015.rpy:942
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_428442c0:

#   l "Did you come back for me, brother-dear?"
    l "¿Volviste por mí, hermano querido?"

# game/episode015.rpy:944
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_e6ea5e7e:

#   l "Did you come back for me, dearest?"
    l "¿Volviste por mí, querida?"

# game/episode015.rpy:948
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_a636e731:

#   c "No, I didn't."
    c "No, no lo hice."

# game/episode015.rpy:950
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_802efcab:

#   l "You came for her, didn't you?"
    l "Viniste por ella, ¿no?"

# game/episode015.rpy:951
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_e7ad40ce:

#   c "Yes, I did."
    c "Sí, lo hice."

# game/episode015.rpy:953
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_80f1ec00:

#   l "Why?!"
    l "¿Por qué?"

# game/episode015.rpy:954
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_a63c415a:

#   l "What do you want with that slut?"
    l "¿Qué quieres con esa zorra?"

# game/episode015.rpy:956
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_d4769ab0:

#   c "She's your sister, Lilly."
    c "Es tu hermana, Lilly."

# game/episode015.rpy:958
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_c9a7dd4c:

#   c "She's your friend, Lilly."
    c "Es tu amiga, Lilly."

# game/episode015.rpy:959
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_78fd3f93:

#   l "I don't care."
    l "No me importa."

# game/episode015.rpy:961
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_8625da14:

#   l "All I care about is you."
    l "Lo único que me importa eres tú."

# game/episode015.rpy:963
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_9564a513:

#   "Lilly advanced on me, her body pressing against mine."
    "Lilly avanzó sobre mí, su cuerpo presionando contra el mío."

# game/episode015.rpy:965
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_d318b76b:

#   l "Why don't we go to my room, so I can show you just how much I care about you."
    l "¿Por qué no vamos a mi habitación? Así podré demostrarte lo mucho que me importas."

# game/episode015.rpy:972
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_29e33a76:

#   "Lilly's smell was intoxicating, and her closeness stirred something inside me."
    "El olor de Lilly era embriagador y su cercanía despertó algo en mi interior."

# game/episode015.rpy:973
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_ab068a80:

#   c "Lead the way."
    c "Abre el camino."

# game/episode015.rpy:976
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_f879bced:

#   c "I can't."
    c "No puedo."

# game/episode015.rpy:978
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_ed0eec76:

#   l "Sure you can."
    l "Claro que sí."

# game/episode015.rpy:980
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_548f80e6:

#   "I pushed open the door to Eva's room."
    "Empujé la puerta de la habitación de Eva."

# game/episode015.rpy:982
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_da5ade18:

#   l "No!"
    l "¡No!"

# game/episode015.rpy:983
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_755ddbaa:

#   "The interior of Eva's bedroom was completely ravaged."
    "El interior del dormitorio de Eva estaba completamente destrozado."

# game/episode015.rpy:984
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_a2cdf865:

#   "Furniture had been smashed, the curtains and tapestries ripped from the wall."
    "Los muebles habían sido destrozados, las cortinas y tapices arrancados de la pared."

# game/episode015.rpy:985
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_91653e96:

#   "The ruin of what was once Eva's bed still stood in the center of the room."
    "La ruina de lo que una vez fue la cama de Eva seguía en pie en el centro de la habitación."

# game/episode015.rpy:987
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_15d1167b:

#   "Eva's lifeless body lay on the bed."
    "El cuerpo sin vida de Eva yacía sobre la cama."

# game/episode015.rpy:988
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_29d9898c:

#   c "What have you done?"
    c "¿Qué has hecho?"

# game/episode015.rpy:990
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_e6a42d45:

#   l "Nothing much...{w} yet..."
    l "No mucho...{w} todavía..."

# game/episode015.rpy:991
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_b53e5930:

#   l "Don't even think of freeing her."
    l "Ni se te ocurra liberarla."

# game/episode015.rpy:993
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_5e233537:

#   c "Why wouldn't I?"
    c "¿Por qué no iba a hacerlo?"

# game/episode015.rpy:994
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_59427dc8:

#   l "Because I'll kill her."
    l "Porque la mataré."

# game/episode015.rpy:995
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_03fc6e71:

#   c "How?!"
    c "¡¿Cómo?!"

# game/episode015.rpy:996
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_7214cfe2:

#   c "Oh..."
    c "Oh..."

# game/episode015.rpy:998
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_572bee63:

#   "Seemingly out of nowhere, Lilly had retrieved a shotgun."
    "Aparentemente de la nada, Lilly había sacado una escopeta."

# game/episode015.rpy:999
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_ed929b28:

#   "I was pretty certain there were no weapons in the house, but Lilly must have been able to manipulate the simulation."
    "Estaba bastante seguro de que no había armas en la casa, pero Lilly debió ser capaz de manipular la simulación."

# game/episode015.rpy:1001
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_c3065977:

#   l "Now, step away from the bed."
    l "Ahora, aléjate de la cama."

# game/episode015.rpy:1002
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_d3d6f820:

#   c "Lilly, what are you going to do?"
    c "Lilly, ¿qué vas a hacer?"

# game/episode015.rpy:1003
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_d9a59ffe:

#   l "Turn around. "
    l "Da la vuelta. "

# game/episode015.rpy:1004
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_c32999c2:

#   l "On your knees, or I'll blow her brains out."
    l "De rodillas, o le vuelo los sesos."

# game/episode015.rpy:1006
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_6b730652:

#   c "She's your sister!"
    c "¡Es tu hermana!"

# game/episode015.rpy:1008
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_9a9a083e:

#   c "She's your friend!"
    c "¡Es tu amiga!"

# game/episode015.rpy:1009
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_0cc6031e:

#   l "On your knees."
    l "De rodillas."

# game/episode015.rpy:1011
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_d363b059:

#   "I complied."
    "Cumplí."

# game/episode015.rpy:1013
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_d0c9480c:

#   "Before I could utter another word, the butt of the rifle connected with my head, and everything went black."
    "Antes de que pudiera pronunciar otra palabra, la culata del rifle conectó con mi cabeza y todo se volvió negro."

# game/episode015.rpy:1019
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_da768f87:

#   l "I knew you'd come back!"
    l "¡Sabía que volverías!"

# game/episode015.rpy:1020
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_80adc58b:

#   l "I've been waiting on you for so long."
    l "Llevo tanto tiempo esperándote."

# game/episode015.rpy:1021
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_35627562:

#   l "All I want is you."
    l "Sólo te quiero a ti."

# game/episode015.rpy:1029
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_8c101356:

#   "Lead the way."
    "Abre el camino."

# game/episode015.rpy:1033
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_18248cc3:

#   "As soon as Lilly let down her guard, I twisted her arm and pacified her."
    "En cuanto Lilly bajó la guardia, le retorcí el brazo y la tranquilicé."

# game/episode015.rpy:1034
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_12fe58ca:

#   c "What have you done to Eva?"
    c "¿Qué le has hecho a Eva?"

# game/episode015.rpy:1036
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_a262d07b:

#   l "Ow, [p_name_short], you're hurting me!"
    l "¡Ay, [p_name_short], me haces daño!"

# game/episode015.rpy:1038
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_27ea1122:

#   c "What have you done with our sister?"
    c "¿Qué has hecho con nuestra hermana?"

# game/episode015.rpy:1040
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_fb1bc0b8:

#   c "What have you done with her?"
    c "¿Qué has hecho con ella?"

# game/episode015.rpy:1041
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_e5c32328:

#   l "Nothing...{w} She's inside."
    l "Nada...{w} Está dentro."

# game/episode015.rpy:1042
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_91c0c7d8:

#   c "Open the door."
    c "Abre la puerta."

# game/episode015.rpy:1044
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_3f2a0437:

#   "Trembling like a leaf, Lilly complied and pushed the door open."
    "Temblando como una hoja, Lilly obedeció y empujó la puerta."

# game/episode015.rpy:1052
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_99dbf0bf:

#   l "See, she's fine."
    l "Ves, ella está bien."

# game/episode015.rpy:1053
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_b61f89fe:

#   c "I wouldn't call that fine."
    c "Yo no lo llamaría bien."

# game/episode015.rpy:1054
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_328068a4:

#   l "She's still breathing, isn't she?"
    l "Todavía respira, ¿verdad?"

# game/episode015.rpy:1057
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_0dcdbe1c:

#   "I pushed my sister into a corner and searched for something to bind her hands."
    "Arrinconé a mi hermana y busqué algo para atarle las manos."

# game/episode015.rpy:1059
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_36cd4ad7:

#   "I pushed Lilly into a corner and searched for something to bind her hands."
    "Arrinconé a Lilly y busqué algo para atarle las manos."

# game/episode015.rpy:1061
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_2ad42a24:

#   "Picking up a length of ripped fabric, I bound her and made her sit down."
    "Cogí un trozo de tela rasgada, la até y la obligué a sentarse."

# game/episode015.rpy:1062
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_bbea13a3:

#   c "Stay there."
    c "Quédate allí."

# game/episode015.rpy:1063
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_22739886:

#   "Lilly stared at me with murder in her eyes while I hasted towards the bed where Eva was lying."
    "Lilly me miró con ojos asesinos mientras yo me apresuraba hacia la cama donde yacía Eva."

# game/episode015.rpy:1065
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_243b6e41:

#   "I made sure she was still breathing first."
    "Primero me aseguré de que seguía respirando."

# game/episode015.rpy:1067
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_f0283bd8:

#   "As I saw her chest rise and fall, I tried to turn her around."
    "Al ver que su pecho subía y bajaba, intenté darle la vuelta."

# game/episode015.rpy:1069
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_83818121:

#   l "Fool!"
    l "¡Idiota!"

# game/episode015.rpy:1071
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_73adf2f4:

#   "Something hard connected with the base of my skull and everything went black."
    "Algo duro conectó con la base de mi cráneo y todo se volvió negro."

# game/episode015.rpy:1075
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_0afeb908:

#   e "Get away from him."
    e "Aléjate de él."

# game/episode015.rpy:1076
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_8229edae:

#   "Gritting her teeth, Lilly complied."
    "Apretando los dientes, Lilly obedeció."

# game/episode015.rpy:1078
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_2ef59959:

#   e "Release him."
    e "Suéltalo."

# game/episode015.rpy:1079
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_a494da55:

#   "Without anybody touching me, the bonds suddenly slipped from my wrists."
    "Sin que nadie me tocara, las ataduras se soltaron de repente de mis muñecas."

# game/episode015.rpy:1080
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_2aef743c:

#   e "Get over here, please, [p_name]."
    e "Ven aquí, por favor, [p_name]."

# game/episode015.rpy:1083
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_d0b44cc2:

#   "I got behind my sister."
    "Me puse detrás de mi hermana."

# game/episode015.rpy:1085
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_b2af4242:

#   "I got behind Eva."
    "Me puse detrás de Eva."

# game/episode015.rpy:1087
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_2347d660:

#   "Lilly was still glaring, ready to make a move."
    "Lilly seguía con la mirada fija, dispuesta a mover ficha."

# game/episode015.rpy:1088
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_4dce4ea5:

#   "Eva started to back away slowly out of the room."
    "Eva empezó a retroceder lentamente fuera de la habitación."

# game/episode015.rpy:1093
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_5b927716:

#   "When we were both out in the hallway, Eva slammed the door shut and pushed a heavy dresser in front of it."
    "Cuando ambos estuvimos en el pasillo, Eva cerró la puerta de un portazo y empujó una pesada cómoda delante de ella."

# game/episode015.rpy:1094
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_1593a219:

#   "I didn't have time to question Eva's sudden strength nor the appearance of such a large piece of furniture that wasn't there before."
    "No tuve tiempo de cuestionar la repentina fuerza de Eva ni la aparición de un mueble tan grande que antes no estaba allí."

# game/episode015.rpy:1096
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_7c555364:

#   e "We have to hurry."
    e "Tenemos que darnos prisa."

# game/episode015.rpy:1098
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_efb7687b:

#   c "But...{w} uh...{w} Eva is still around here somewhere."
    c "Pero...{w} uh...{w} Eva todavía está por aquí en alguna parte."

# game/episode015.rpy:1100
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_e07df9c3:

#   c "But...{w} uh...{w} Eva is still in there."
    c "Pero...{w} uh...{w} Eva sigue ahí dentro."

# game/episode015.rpy:1101
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_4a6d2ef3:

#   e "She won't harm her."
    e "No le hará daño."

# game/episode015.rpy:1102
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_67898a3d:

#   e "Lilly hasn't slipped that far...{w} yet."
    e "Lilly no ha llegado tan lejos...{w} todavía."

# game/episode015.rpy:1104
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_e21e0681:

#   "Together, we ran down the stairs outside onto the mansion's grounds."
    "Juntos, bajamos corriendo las escaleras hasta los terrenos de la mansión."

# game/episode015.rpy:1106
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_c0ad0f22:

#   "Eva ran toward the formal gardens that had wilted and died in my absence."
    "Eva corrió hacia los jardines formales que se habían marchitado y muerto en mi ausencia."

# game/episode015.rpy:1108
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_17750543:

#   "We took refuge in the stone gazebo in the center of the gardens."
    "Nos refugiamos en el cenador de piedra del centro de los jardines."

# game/episode015.rpy:1110
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_b35ab4bf:

#   e "It will take her a while to get here."
    e "Tardará un poco en llegar."

# game/episode015.rpy:1111
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_077bf075:

#   e "She's less strong outside than inside the house."
    e "Es menos fuerte fuera que dentro de casa."

# game/episode015.rpy:1112
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_8f587dd6:

#   c "What happened, Eva?"
    c "¿Qué pasó, Eva?"

# game/episode015.rpy:1114
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_819e3008:

#   e "After Lilly lost her mind and you suddenly left, things got...{w} weird."
    e "Después de que Lilly perdiera la cabeza y tú te fueras de repente, las cosas se pusieron...{w} raro."

# game/episode015.rpy:1115
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_3778dcaa:

#   e "I don't know how, but I got out of my room, chased by Lilly."
    e "No sé cómo, pero salí de mi habitación, perseguido por Lilly."

# game/episode015.rpy:1116
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_1f048a22:

#   e "First, I tried to hide, but she found me every time."
    e "Primero, intenté esconderme, pero ella me encontraba siempre."

# game/episode015.rpy:1118
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_22b00353:

#   e "That's when I realized she was able to do all those crazy things."
    e "Fue entonces cuando me di cuenta de que era capaz de hacer todas esas locuras."

# game/episode015.rpy:1119
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_b8b4afa7:

#   e "She could summon objects, physically manipulate things, seemingly at will."
    e "Podía invocar objetos, manipular cosas físicamente, aparentemente a voluntad."

# game/episode015.rpy:1120
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_5e771358:

#   e "At first I couldn’t believe my eyes, but Lilly proved time and time again that she had gotten these strange powers."
    e "Al principio no podía creer lo que veía, pero Lilly demostró una y otra vez que había conseguido esos extraños poderes."

# game/episode015.rpy:1121
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_446364ee:

#   e "So, feeling like a fool, I tried to do the same, without much luck at first."
    e "Así que, sintiéndome como un tonto, intenté hacer lo mismo, sin mucha suerte al principio."

# game/episode015.rpy:1123
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_7f25d62f:

#   e "But then, I made something appear."
    e "Pero entonces, hice aparecer algo."

# game/episode015.rpy:1125
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_c05cca13:

#   e "It took almost all my willpower and I nearly passed out."
    e "Me costó casi toda mi fuerza de voluntad y estuve a punto de desmayarme."

# game/episode015.rpy:1126
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_3d9550d2:

#   e "By then, I'd concluded the house wasn't safe for me and fled outside."
    e "Para entonces, había llegado a la conclusión de que la casa no era segura para mí y huí fuera."

# game/episode015.rpy:1127
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_438bdf2b:

#   e "Lilly hounded me, and it came to a stand-off near the edge of the grounds."
    e "Lilly me acosó, y se llegó a un enfrentamiento cerca del límite del terreno."

# game/episode015.rpy:1128
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_5a792f39:

#   e "She summoned knives to hurl at me, while I conjured a ball of force to overwhelm her."
    e "Ella invocó cuchillos para lanzármelos, mientras yo conjuraba una bola de fuerza para arrollarla."

# game/episode015.rpy:1129
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_6a15f787:

#   e "We both struck true."
    e "Ambos dimos en el clavo."

# game/episode015.rpy:1130
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_78dbf736:

#   e "The knife grazed my face as the wave of energy drove Lilly into the ground."
    e "El cuchillo me rozó la cara mientras la onda de energía clavaba a Lilly en el suelo."

# game/episode015.rpy:1131
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_53b1e0b9:

#   e "I fled further into the gardens and Lilly retreated towards the house."
    e "Yo huí más hacia los jardines y Lilly se retiró hacia la casa."

# game/episode015.rpy:1132
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_87e08486:

#   c "Did she come back?"
    c "¿Ha vuelto?"

# game/episode015.rpy:1134
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_e26be94f:

#   e "She did."
    e "Lo hizo."

# game/episode015.rpy:1135
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_695cacaa:

#   e "Sometimes we met here in the gardens, or she caught me snooping around the house."
    e "A veces nos veíamos aquí, en los jardines, o me pillaba husmeando por la casa."

# game/episode015.rpy:1136
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_0f46e45b:

#   e "We fought on both occasions."
    e "Luchamos en ambas ocasiones."

# game/episode015.rpy:1138
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_23b1b70b:

#   e "My power to manipulate the world isn't as strong near the house."
    e "Mi poder para manipular el mundo no es tan fuerte cerca de casa."

# game/episode015.rpy:1139
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_0fd2ab1b:

#   e "I guess it's the same for Lilly as she ventures further away from the mansion."
    e "Supongo que lo mismo le ocurre a Lilly cuando se aleja de la mansión."

# game/episode015.rpy:1140
translate spanish ep015_sim_altered_89ca43e0:

#   c "What were you hoping to accomplish by returning to the house?"
